'''變聲器'''又稱'''语音变换器'''，是指一种改变錄音者的[[語音|語音]]或其他人的[[語音|語音]]的[[音调|音调]]、[[音高|音高]]以達到聲音[[失真|失真]]的電子设备或軟件<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Voice conversion through vector quantization|last=Abe|first=M.|last2=Nakamura|first2=S.|date=April 1988|journal=ICASSP-88., International Conference on Acoustics, Speech, and Signal Processing|doi=10.1109/ICASSP.1988.196671|pages=655–658 vol.1|last3=Shikano|first3=K.|last4=Kuwabara|first4=H.}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=High quality voice morphing|last=Hui Ye|last2=Young|first2=S.|date=May 2004|journal=2004 IEEE International Conference on Acoustics, Speech, and Signal Processing|doi=10.1109/ICASSP.2004.1325909|volume=1|pages=I–9|isbn=0-7803-8484-9}}</ref>。變聲器可以讓男声变成女声，或讓女声变成男声。男女變聲的核心因素是音调，變聲器通過修改聲音音調以達到男女變聲的效果<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Voice morphing: An illusion or reality|last=Ahmed|first=I.|last2=Sadiq|first2=A.|date=February 2018|journal=2018 International Conference on Advancements in Computational Sciences (ICACS)|doi=10.1109/ICACS.2018.8333282|pages=1–6|isbn=978-1-5386-2172-1|last3=Atif|first3=M.|last4=Naseer|first4=M.|last5=Adnan|first5=M.}}</ref>。

